知點解佢哋唔喺唱榮光集會嘅時候吹雞搞事?<br />\n知唔知點解佢哋唔喺組團修牆嘅時候吹雞搞事?<br />\n知唔知點解佢哋唔喺大遊行嘅時候吹雞搞事?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">因為佢哋知自己吹雞唔夠人會俾人打返轉頭啊</span></span><br />\n連藍絲都識敵進我退,去淘大嗰班就唔識,明知冇PLAN好一定唔撚夠人都照衝,重蠢過藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋唔使再問遊行有警察係咪唔去<br />\n屌你咩每次遊行宣傳咗幾耐?有PLAN定有事前計劃咪會夠人囉,夠人咪去囉<br />\n朝早宣佈下晝有遊行,然後現場有幾百隻狗等你,你都唔撚去啦<br />\nbe water唔代表啲water識瞬間移動啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今日去淘大嗰班&quot;手足&quot;,同825嗰隻藍衫的士佬一樣咁戇鳩</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cUkUVtU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcUkUVtU.gif&h=8cdf3b14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真係以為藍絲企定定俾你打,以為自己可以一打十咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b2fa668a0135bc31020e118366c8e3c8218ab8e","tid":1568510,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:09:15.000Z","msg":"日撚日比人帶風向"},{"pid":"d5a3f23df710653eaf07c2478989d795e3ae8687","tid":1568510,"uid":201374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:09:44.000Z","msg":"由頭到尾都唔撚知理班廢老做乜尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca645d2b8e7466cae015e277c4ce1597e4e6cf12","tid":1568510,"uid":157938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:10:15.000Z","msg":"連儂牆 AIRDROP<br />\n<br />\n915 915 915 915 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d52d1b